    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在这款类肉鸽卡组构筑游戏中探索德雷克陨落的世界。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构建你的卡组，发现强大的道具，穿越沼泽与山巅，一场充满熟悉玩法的奇幻旅程等你开启。  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎留下你对《德雷克陨落》的看法！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们非常想听听你的反馈与建议。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/e9930edd049843896e4c843a25a53621.poster.avif?t=1760389515\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/e9930edd049843896e4c843a25a53621.webm?t=1760389515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/e9930edd049843896e4c843a25a53621.mp4?t=1760389515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重塑破碎之物：世界构架</strong><br>在每一次征程中做出策略性的卡牌选择！探索并收集数百张卡牌，构筑属于你的套牌，征服破碎的德雷克陨落世界。挑选彼此协同的卡牌，才能有效击败敌人，挑战统治一切的巨龙。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/fbb53853b46f9f8966020e00107bbb7e.poster.avif?t=1760389515\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/fbb53853b46f9f8966020e00107bbb7e.webm?t=1760389515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/fbb53853b46f9f8966020e00107bbb7e.mp4?t=1760389515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不断进化的卡组构筑</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每一次征程中做出策略性的卡牌选择！探索并收集数百张卡牌，构筑你的套牌，征服破碎的德雷克陨落世界。挑选彼此协同的卡牌，才能有效击败敌人，挑战巨龙。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/378c8e6bd61095931ed7dd35caab1491.poster.avif?t=1760389515\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/378c8e6bd61095931ed7dd35caab1491.webm?t=1760389515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/378c8e6bd61095931ed7dd35caab1491.mp4?t=1760389515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态变化的世界</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    每一次穿越破碎的德雷克陨落之旅都是独一无二的。你可以选择危险或安全的道路，遭遇各式敌      人，挑选不同卡牌，发现独特遗物，并在每次旅途中面对全新的挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/d16e5bec6dd71c93425d3cd452b9139c.poster.avif?t=1760389515\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/d16e5bec6dd71c93425d3cd452b9139c.webm?t=1760389515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/d16e5bec6dd71c93425d3cd452b9139c.mp4?t=1760389515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>星辰之力，尽在掌握</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与神秘的“星界契印”仪式，引导天体能量以获得强大的增益效果。随着你不断攀升，每层楼带来的加成将愈发强大，为你提供关键的战略优势。把握正确时机激活星辰之力，引导你踏上通往德雷克陨落的命运之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/5bdf578088e24443356ce63a5daa85d4.poster.avif?t=1760389515\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/5bdf578088e24443356ce63a5daa85d4.webm?t=1760389515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/5bdf578088e24443356ce63a5daa85d4.mp4?t=1760389515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多变世界，遍历群境</strong><br>穿越各异的生态区域，每个区域都带来独特的挑战与丰厚的回报。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/dec8e0ed68f4b8a3c13853f08c22f286.poster.avif?t=1760389515\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/dec8e0ed68f4b8a3c13853f08c22f286.webm?t=1760389515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/dec8e0ed68f4b8a3c13853f08c22f286.mp4?t=1760389515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
